     H            Y.
     F** UTLR31C  ****************************************************
     F*  PROGRAM    : GET PART NAME BY PART#                         *
     F*  WRITTEN    : J.WATANABE    2022.03.16                       *
     F*----------------------------------------------------*
     F*  CALLING SEQ.
     F*                    CALL 'UTLR31C'
     F*                    PARM           $SHIN  12
     F*                    PARM           $NAME  15
     F*   IN  $SHIN : 12A IAF PART#
     F*   OUT $NAME : 15A PART NAME
     F****************************************************************
     FFCEPL01 IF  E           K        DISK
      *---------------------------------------------------------------
     I            DS
     I                                        1  12 K2SHIN
     I                                        1   5 K2SHN1
     I                                        6  10 K2SHN2
     I                                       11  12 K2SHN3
     I           SDS
     I                                        1   8 #PGM
     I                                      244 253 #WSID
     I                                      254 263 #USER
      ******************************************************
      *                    MAIN PROCESS
      ******************************************************
     C           *ENTRY    PLIST
     C                     PARM           $SHIN  12
     C                     PARM           $NAME  15
     C                     MOVE *BLANK    $NAME
      *
     C           K#01      KLIST
     C                     KFLD           K2SHN1
     C                     KFLD           K2SHN2
     C                     KFLD           K2SHN3
      *
     C                     MOVEL$SHIN     K2SHIN
     C           K#01      CHAINFCEPL01              91
     C           *IN91     IFEQ *OFF
     C                     MOVELA2SMEI    $NAME
     C                     ENDIF
      *
     C                     MOVE *ON       *INLR
     C                     RETRN
